headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week's Prize Ride: The Albany Roosevelt
content: Maybe the only love in your life is the road, in which case dedicated LS Car Meet members who win a Street Race Series race three days in a row will earn the keys to the Albany Roosevelt seen parked atop the Slamtruck at the heart of the meet. This historic limousine is so classic, so timeless, it could be in a museum.
